    "Provincial supplements conflated where adapters are ready: NS NSTDB, NB Forest Roads, AB Access, ON MNRF, QC chemins multiusages, BC FTEN (when ingest completes).",
    "OSM motorized highways are the road fabric (motorized_permissive). Shortbread tiles remain display-only; POIs are a separate pack.",
